---
layout: default
title: "Contact"
description: "Get in touch with Rose City Robotics — email us or visit our studio in downtown Portland."
permalink: /contact/
---

<%= render SimpleLayout.new(eyebrow: "Contact", title: "Reach the team", intro: "Email is the fastest way to reach us — we read every message. Or find us in downtown Portland.") do %>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:gap-12">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <p class="eyebrow text-primary-600">Email us</p>
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@rosecityrobotics.com"
        class="group mt-3 inline-flex items-baseline gap-2 rounded text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 transition-colors hover:text-primary-600 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 sm:text-3xl"
      >
        <span class="border-b-2 border-primary-500/70 group-hover:border-primary-600">hello@rosecityrobotics.com</span>
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none translate-y-1 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1 motion-reduce:transition-none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">We usually reply within a couple of business days.</p>

      <div class="my-8 h-px bg-gray-200"></div>

      <p class="eyebrow text-primary-600">Visit</p>
      <address class="mt-3 text-lg not-italic leading-7 text-gray-700">
        <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Rose City Robotics</span><br />
        111 SW 5th Ave, 5th Floor<br />
        Portland, OR 97204
      </address>
      <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider text-gray-500">45.5222° N · 122.6789° W</p>
      <a
        href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=111+SW+5th+Ave%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97204"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-link mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-0"
      >
        Get directions
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7 17 17 7M7 7h10v10" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-3">
      <div class="h-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <iframe
          title="Map to Rose City Robotics — 111 SW 5th Ave, Portland, OR 97204"
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2795.3995797807765!2d-122.67889932348919!3d45.52216407107509!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x54950a06b198f96b%3A0x83a60dc1c0cfa1f9!2sU.S.%20Bancorp%20Tower!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1783357336996!5m2!1sen!2sus"
          class="h-full min-h-[360px] w-full border-0 lg:min-h-[440px]"
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
